{"word":"G562 - ἀπέραντος - apérantos - ap-er'-an-tos - Endless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπέραντος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apérantos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-er'-an-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Endless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முடிவில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"that cannot be passed through, boundless, endless"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a secondary derivative of <a href=\"#/G4008 - πέραν - péran - per'-an/4008\">G4008</a>; <i>unfinished</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>interminable:</i> - endless.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}